			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">The project is aimed at introducing schoolchildren and members of the general public to the basic science of-..music and illustrate how modern research is contributing to the study and development of musical'instruments. A travelling roadshow consisting on hands-on exhibits, with associated talks and displays, willvisit primary schools, secondary schools and science festivals. Participants will be able to study the natureof their own speaking and singing voice using a spectroscopic display, and to see how acoustic pulses can beused to visualise the inside of a trumpet. Surprising air flow patterns around organ pipes will be madevisible using laser beams.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
